<div class="permission-explanations">
  <h4>What does the different permissions mean?</h4>

  <dl class="explanation">
    <dt>Reviewers:</dt>
    <dd>Can update merge request statuses</dd>
    <dd>Will receive notifications on new merge requests</dd>

    <dt>Committers:</dt>
    <dd>Can push commits to the repository</dd>

    <dt>Administrators:</dt>
    <dd>Can edit the repository name, description and settings</dd>
    <dd>Can manage collaborators</dd>
    <dd>Can delete the repository</dd>
  </dl>
  <p class="hint">Note that the permissions doesn't cascade down, meaning
    that for instance a committer isn't automatically a reviewer</p>
</div>
